Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, openssl
Description: Domain-specific language for blockchain and backend engineering
 Vorlang is a typed, expression-oriented systems language designed
 specifically for building decentralized applications, secure backend
 services, and robust command-line tools.
 .
 Features include:
  - Full OOP support with classes, methods, and inheritance
  - Native blockchain types (Block, Transaction, Wallet)
  - Cryptographic functions (SHA-256, RSA, AES-256)
  - Comprehensive standard library
  - Modern syntax with if/else, while, for-each loops
